    </div></div><p>LastPass nails its sign-up flow by highlighting its key benefits without distracting users. They use short phrases and clean design to remind you why you&#x27;re signing up. As a password manager, LastPass smartly asks you to create a Master password right away. They even provide tips and strength indicators to help you make it secure. It&#x27;s a great balance of showcasing <a href="defining-your-product-value-proposition-tips-and-examples">value proposition</a> and guiding users through an important setup step.</p><h3>Linear</h3><p>Linear provides three ways to sign up for their service: </p><h4>With Google</h4><div class="w-embed"><div class="wrap-slider-blog">
