    </div></div><p>Mural basically follows best UX practices for their sign-up process, similar to those we’ve discussed already. There are two features, however, that grab our attention:</p><ul role="list"><li>Appealing illustrations that give the app a lovely aesthetic</li><li>A smooth transition from sign-up to personalization, where users create their workspace</li></ul><p>This smart approach means that once you&#x27;ve signed up, you&#x27;ll see recommendations for relevant templates. It&#x27;s a great way to help users quickly get started with Mural.</p><h3>PayUp</h3><div class="w-embed"><div class="wrap-slider-blog">
