    </div></div><p>This Invision screen layout design demonstrates the sign-in with the team domain. Nothing much different from a standard practice, but it still demonstrates that there can be different options for this flow.</p><h2>Onboarding</h2><p>There are so many different <a href="user-onboarding-ux-patterns-a-guide-for-saas-companies">user onboarding UX patterns for SaaS products</a>, depending on your specific case. Below, we’ll try to cover the most popular ones with our UI screen design examples.</p><h3>Marvel</h3><div class="w-embed"><div class="wrap-slider-blog">
