    </div></div><p>Framer web builder uses <strong>a</strong> <strong>video tour</strong> as an onboarding for their customers. As for a product whose features are not immediately intuitive, a video simplifies and visually explains the steps and serves its purpose effectively.</p><p>Framer’s video tour is well integrated into the app. Users can control if they want to watch it, see the number of steps left and can easily replay the step if needed. </p><h3>ProcessPlace</h3><div class="w-embed"><div class="wrap-slider-blog">
