    </div></div><p><a href="../cases/process-place">Process Place</a> is a workflow management app for HR professionals for whom we at Eleken created a user onboarding experience in the form of <strong>a guided checklist</strong>. Here are its main benefits:</p><ul role="list"><li>It starts with a choice: follow a guided checklist or explore freely. </li><li>The onboarding is designed as an engaging to-do list, motivating users to complete each step. </li><li>Clear instructions and playful elements (like clapping sheep) keep users engaged. </li><li>After finishing, a congratulatory pop-up appears with suggestions for next steps, smoothly transitioning users from onboarding to active product use. </li></ul><p>This approach balances guidance with flexibility, ensuring users feel supported as they start using the platform. If you like what we did for ProcessPlace, learn more about our <a href="../ui-ux-design-services">UI/UX design services</a>.</p><h3>Hubspot</h3><div class="w-embed"><div class="wrap-slider-blog">
