    </div></div><p>Hubspot onboarding shows a well-designed example of <strong>an app tour</strong>. They offer users the ability to complete eight tasks, guiding them with tooltips. What is important about this design is that </p><ul role="list"><li>Block with onboarding tasks does not overlap the interface</li><li>there’s a progress bar indicating how much work is already done</li><li>users can skip the tour if they want </li></ul><h3>Any.do</h3><div class="w-embed"><div class="wrap-slider-blog">
      <div class="swiper swiper-initialized swiper-horizontal swiper-backface-hidden">
