    </div></div><p><a href="../cases/prift">Prift</a>, a personal finance management app, is one of Eleken&#x27;s clients for whom we helped create an MVP. The app allows users to add their current pension savings and predict the size of their pension investments by retirement. Users can connect to their pension provider or enter the information manually.</p><p>This design simplifies a complex, secure process, making it intuitive and user-friendly. To enhance convenience, we included logos of different pension providers, not just their names, so users can quickly recognize and select the right one.</p><h3>Freshsales – add a new contact</h3><div class="w-embed"><div class="wrap-slider-blog">
