    </div></div><p>Global search design is interesting because it has not only regular search bar, but also latest search list, which helps you quickly repeat recent lookups and extra options, like Created by, or Date, that serve to enhance the user experience by providing targeted search capabilities.</p><h3>Todoist</h3><div class="w-embed"><div class="wrap-slider-blog">
